      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 109,
      "message": "This part of the code that you highlighted is dealing with the yang resources that are already in the db (So basically this is creating a relation between the schema set and the already existing resources).\n\nThe part of the code that adds new yang resources is in line 102. To answer your question about duplicates. When a yang resource already exists in the db, we don't add it to the db. All this is taken care of by the storeSchemaSet method in the CpsModulePersistenceService.",
